-- Gilbert Arenas Signs With Yao Ming’s Shanghai Sharks, News Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-11-13T02:28:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-13/gilbert-arenas-signs-with-yao-ming-s-shanghai-sharks-news-says.html
Former National Basketball
Association All-Star point guard  Gilbert Arenas  has signed a
contract to play for Yao Ming’s Shanghai Sharks team, the
Beijing News  reported  today, without citing anyone.  The deal will be announced soon, the newspaper reported,
without providing additional details. Arenas has been in
Shanghai for one week with the team, according to the report.  The Shanghai Sharks, which Yao bought in 2009, had already
signed former  Charlotte  Bobcat power forward D.J. White.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
Alfred Cang in Shanghai at 
 acang@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Liu at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  